Course is dedicated for students who wish continue after two years introductory course their research in immunology. Course gives to students additional knowledge in immunological research. Particular attention is paid on modern molecular immunology methods. As a result of the course students will write a full scientific paper.Objectives/eesmärkid:  To get general principles of research in immunology (III stage).Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  At the end of the course, within the syllabus, a student:  1. knows safety principles for laboratory investigations; 2. knows how to use selected immunological methods to get answer for scientific questions; 3. knows elementary methods used in statistical analysis of laboratory investigations results; 4. knows how to make oral presentation.
